# PromptKit

A lightweight interactive command-line utility for structured prompting.

## Install
pip install promptkit

## Setup
Set environment variable:

Windows (PowerShell):
setx PROMPTKIT_KEY "your_api_key"

Linux / macOS:
export PROMPTKIT_KEY="your_api_key"

## Run
promptkit
